widgets_values:
If your Upscale Model is 4x, set the Image Resize "Rescale Factor" to 0.5 for 2x upscale of the original size.

1x model x 0.5 factor = 0.5x downsacle 
4x model x 0.5 factor = 2x upscale
8x model x 0.5 factor = 4x upscale

nodes.title: Sampler 2 Upscale Method: 1 = latent up, 2 = pixels up
